 class=\"line\">   .from(<span class=\"string\">\"Hi &#123;first_name&#125;, your are &#123;age&#125; years old.\"</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">   .put(<span class=\"string\">\"first_name\"</span>, firstName)</span><br><span class=\"line\">   .put(<span class=\"string\">\"age\"</span>, age)</span><br><span class=\"line\">   .format();</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// Flavored Usage</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">CharSequence formatted = Kirai</span><br><span class=\"line\">   .from(<span class=\"string\">\"Hi &#123;first_name&#125;, your are &#123;age&#125; years old.\"</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">   .put(Piece.put(<span class=\"string\">\"first_name\"</span>, firstName).bold().italic().big())</span><br><span class=\"line\">   .put(Piece.put(<span class=\"string\">\"age\"</span>, age).underline().color(<span class=\"string\">\"#FF0000\"</span>))</span><br><span class=\"line\">   .format();</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">textView.setText(formatted);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"Download\"><a href=\"#Download\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Download\"></a>Download</h2><p>You can depend on this library through Maven: </p>\n<figure class=\"highlight xml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">dependency</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">groupId</span>&gt;</span>com.github.pwittchen.kirai<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">groupId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span>library<span